content: My God! I've been a huge fan of the pumped series and I can't believe it took me this long to find here about this game! 100% best bmx game on the market. So much fun. The previous offering Pumped 3, is a great. What made it difficult is boosting high enough to transfer effectively enough to clear the next gap. This game is also fun and enjoyable. What makes it difficult is steering. That's the challenge. The trail hard to see as it is in front of the rider and poorly contrasted. The lower left and right corners control everything. It's a design that seems to lack polish. There are no joysticks, just spots swipe and tap. It's a fun game, but the controls suck.
